# Autonocraft Rendering

Key files: `Engine/WorldRenderer.cs`, `Engine/HudRenderer.cs`, `Engine/Renderer.cs`, `Content/BlockEffect.fx`.

After rendering changes:
1. Run `dotnet run --project src/Autonocraft -- --test`
2. Visual check with screenshot workflow:
   ```bash
   dotnet run --project src/Autonocraft -- --skip-menu
   python3 tests/interact.py screenshot render_check.png
   ```

Regenerate atlas after texture changes: `dotnet run --project src/Autonocraft.AtlasBuild`
